(firstQuint)Autologous Bone Marrow Stem Cells Transplantation in Patients With Temporal Lobe Epilepsy.

 The aim of this study is to evaluate autologous bone marrow stem cells transplantation as a safe and potentially beneficial treatment for patients with temporal lobe refractory epilepsy.

 We are mainly evaluating seizure frequency, hippocampal volume an cognitive performance.

